@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@secret = troque-este-secret

### Add Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transacao
Authorization: Bearer {{secret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "valor": 100.0,
  "dataHora": "2026-02-19T21:07:34.011Z"
}

### Clear Transactions
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transacao
Authorization: Bearer {{secret}}

### Get Statistics (com intervalo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/estatistica?intervaloBusca=600
Authorization: Bearer {{secret}}

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Authorization: Bearer {{secret}}

### OpenAPI JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

### Scalar UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs
